"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"老實說，這個問題挺拔辣的，但我看『[九宮奇門](https://www.books.com.tw/exep/assp.php/caishin/products/0010887898?sloc=main&utm_source=caishin&utm_medium=ap-books&utm_content=recommend&utm_campaign=ap-202110)』這本書內有講到可以抓方位，那就來測試看看。\\n\\n這個問題我是在2021年10月15日下午15:35分占測，得到的奇門遁甲盤為：\\n\\n![](https://assets.matters.news/embed/bab847ac-f695-4452-bb3d-89b80f335ed1.png)\\n\\n按照『[九宮奇門](https://www.books.com.tw/exep/assp.php/caishin/products/0010887898?sloc=main&utm_source=caishin&utm_medium=ap-books&utm_content=recommend&utm_campaign=ap-202110)』這本書內第51頁的吉凶分數表格來算分數。\\n\\n使用刪去法後得到乾方跟坎方是好方位，於是就把拍照用手機帶好就朝著住家的乾方走去，大概是台北港的位置。\\n\\n沿路拍了許多照片，也確實有拍到一張我相當滿意的照片：\\n\\n![](https://assets.matters.news/embed/c280ada9-14cf-4c38-a6f8-85711802e011.jpeg)\\n\\n \\n \",\"timestamp\":1642607930,\"title\":\"『九宮奇門使用紀錄』往哪個方向會拍到我滿意的照片？\"},\"digest\":\"aALuXzhHuHljDLMT8B2Un8O7rvK9kR52Lonp3ws4xsc\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xC6fEb0bf7Bc1D065c944734C4032a240b5aB2DAc\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dQgTHZeUZm4untVZrW4z_rM8TQMDGmQxxlSKcxjBiJQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"8XzyfMIYpaOj6ZgPyot13O09GbWlrbRdWcvEveNQ4UQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ekVOmiT77_CuFLOZnX07v6aaV0x6foBWSWtp37zwcsAwm1E1LCcVuE2KeiR1LpFcHTWmMjaUYKnzqYun0uzMaA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x87692e1c30fa825eb3bcc03e495bcbaaeb2a7878cb492c6f433e7d9075d7043c6a3a5b2a4834b82f26a6f875255a7a4cdbfbac1162ad1cdb9234cc4e717a5b3d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dQgTHZeUZm4untVZrW4z_rM8TQMDGmQxxlSKcxjBiJQ\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"8XzyfMIYpaOj6ZgPyot13O09GbWlrbRdWcvEveNQ4UQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"aALuXzhHuHljDLMT8B2Un8O7rvK9kR52Lonp3ws4xsc\"}"